Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.75,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}I've been ignoring everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.05,EN-op,,0,0,0,,I've been wandering around
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.05,0:01:42.45,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I've been deceived everything. At that time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.81,0:01:47.50,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Then you appeared in front of me. You ignited my pale heart
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.52,0:01:51.80,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}We've been looking for each other from now on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.82,0:01:53.01,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Save you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.16,0:01:58.60,JP-op,,0,0,0,,際限ない犠牲を
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.08,0:02:03.98,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}朦朧とした理想を
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.73,JP-op,,0,0,0,,もう無駄にしないようにと
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.73,0:02:12.35,JP-op,,0,0,0,,悲しみを切り刻んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.37,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.37,0:02:18.60,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.62,0:02:22.79,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Just now. Chip at your heart. We just fight for freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.92,0:02:27.50,JP-op,,0,0,0,,奪い合って　汚し合って
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.69,JP-op,,0,0,0,,それでも守りたくて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.86,0:02:34.09,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.09,0:02:37.55,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.56,0:02:42.06,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}We don't want to go through that again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.06,0:02:47.63,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}時は満ちた　始まりの鐘が鳴る
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.59,0:02:54.66,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}Get away from me
